一、Windows

1、 http://dl.google.com/android/ndk/android-ndk-r9d-windows-x86_64.zip
	https://dl-ssl.google.com//android/repository/latest_usb_driver_windows.zip

2、 python setup.py
	NDK_ROOT = d:\adt-bundle-windows-x86\android-ndk-r8e
	ANDROID_SDK_ROOT = D:\adt-bundle-windows-x86\sdk
	ANT_ROOT = d:\adt-bundle-windows-x86\apache-ant-1.9.3\bin
	COCOS_CONSOLE_ROOT=F:\cocos2dx\cocos2d-x-3.0rc0\tools/cocos2d-console/bin

3、 JAVA_HOME
	C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.7.0_25
	CLASSPATH
	.;%JAVA_HOME%\lib\tools.jar;%JAVA_HOME%\lib\dt.jar;%JAVA_HOME%\lib;
	PATH
	.;%JAVA_HOME%\bin;%ANDROID_SDK_ROOT%\tools;%ANDROID_SDK_ROOT%\platform-tools;

4、 C:\WINDOWS\system32\drivers\etc\hosts
	203.208.46.146 dl.google.com
	203.208.46.146 dl-ssl.google.com

5、 在SDK Manager下Tools->Options打开了SDK Manager的Settings，
    选中“Force https://… sources to be fetched using http://…”，强制使用http协议。

6、 cocos new mbclient -p com.wanmei.mbclient -l cpp -d wanmei
	cocos compile -p android -j 4 --ap 20
	adb install -r some.apk
	adb logcat
	
二、Macosx
	
1、 sudo ln -s "/Applications/CMake.app/Contents/bin/cmake" /usr/bin/cmake

2、 /Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdkXXXXX.jdk/Contents/Info.plist
	<key>JVMCapabilities</key>
	<array>
　　	<string>JNI</string>
　　	<string>BundledApp</string>
　　	<string>WebStart</string>
　　	<string>Applets</string>
　　	<string>CommandLine</string>
	</array>

3、 sudo vi /etc/hosts

